title: Daniel Fang from Turnstile, Mindset and Praise
itunes:title: Daniel Fang from Turnstile, Mindset and Praise
description:
Concluding our themed month is a conversation with one of the most prolific drummers around currently in hardcore, Daniel Fang. He splits his time up between Turnstile, Mindset and Praise. We had a very deep conversation about education, being active in so many bands and authenticity. It's a great conversation and one that deserves your time. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
